snippet.title: LesbiAnts: Our New Morphology - Trailer (Steam/itch.io)
snippet.description:
LesbiAnts - Our New Morphology is already available on itch.io here:
https://astoryinpieces.itch.io/lesbiantsgb

And you can wishlist it on Steam where it will release in March 2024:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2773120/LesbiAnts__Our_New_Morphology/

A small colony of exiled queens, living out life imitating what they knew, suddenly disrupted by an unnatural infestation...

"It's like a mostly-straight-faced B-movie with sci-fi erotica vibes, but about ants!"

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/astoryinpieces
